{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"690f3eb2b2","title":"在中共中央政治局会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"acf22f190b","index":0,"year":1939,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"690f3eb2b2"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6daa8ec288","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局会议上的讲话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"690f3eb2b2"},{"id":"9a752f263f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年7月3日）这些文件指出反共、防共、限共，我认为防共、限共是国民党的防御口号，要强调反对内战危险，指出反共危险便是内战。这些文件中，都要强调反对内战。宣言中的文字要简洁些，纲领每条只要一两句话。[1]这是毛泽东在中共中央致治局会议上讨论中共中央为纪念抗战两周年对时局宜言和致国民党带等文件时话话的一部分。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"690f3eb2b2"}],"page":{"id":"4857981383","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"690f3eb2b2","start":475,"end":475}}}},"__N_SSG":true}